  "prompt": "What are some small restaurant chains in Dallas? (under 10 locations)",
  "response": "Here are some small restaurant chains in Dallas with under ten locations:\n\n1. **Malai Kitchen** - A blend of Thai and Indian cuisines, known for its unique dishes and vibrant atmosphere.\n\n2. **Caf\u00e9 Brazil** - A cozy caf\u00e9 specializing in coffee and American breakfast dishes with a Brazilian twist.\n\n3. **Smoky John's BBQ** - A family-run barbecue joint that offers impressive smoked meats and Southern comfort food.\n\n4. **Jasper\u2019s** - A casual yet upscale chain focusing on American comfort food with a modern twist, ideal for a variety of dining occasions.\n\n5. **CiboDivino Marketplace** - A marketplace and restaurant that offers Italian-inspired cuisine with a focus on fresh ingredients and artisanal products.\n\n6. **Taco Diner** - A vibrant eatery serving gourmet tacos and Tex-Mex favorites in a lively setting.\n\n7. **Buzzbrews Kitchen** - Known for its eclectic menu of breakfast, lunch, and dinner offerings, this restaurant is particularly famous for its breakfast served all day.\n\n8. **Dine-In at Dallas** - A small chain focusing on gourmet comfort food with a local flair and an emphasis on fresh ingredients.\n\nThese restaurants showcase a variety of cuisines and dining styles, contributing to the diverse culinary scene in Dallas.",
